Piggyback With Meade ETX-90
Astro

<p>I found a cheap way to build my own piggyback mount for my etx-90. All I needed was (Price in CHF):
<ul>
 	<li>Clamp 10.4cm diameter(7.-)</li>
 	<li>Super Glue (4.-)</li>
 	<li>M6 Metal Screw (0.70)</li>
</ul>
</p>

<p>Here you can see how I assembled everything.</p>

